{"tid":1038922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【財政預算案】即日起提高創科研究員津貼　資助中學獲100萬元買IT設備","createTime":"2019-02-27T05:08:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T11:50:24.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"69b959e15c8217213727b876e8ca1520ebe59db9","tid":1038922,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190227/s00001/c2f20c97c4af771ec89b89265c4275aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190227%2Fs00001%2Fc2f20c97c4af771ec89b89265c4275aa.jpg&h=d46e2583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n財政司長陳茂波在立法會宣讀新一份《財政預算案》。在創科教育方面，陳茂波表示，為鼓勵學校推行科普教育和培養本地科技人才，政府將動用5億元，在未來3個學年推動「中學IT創新實驗室」計劃，向每間資助中學提供100萬元，以自行購置所需資訊科技設備、專業服務與舉辦課外活動，加深同學對人工智能、大數據等認識。<br />\n<br />\n大學方面，陳茂波指出，將預留160億元專款供教資會資助的大學，增建或翻新校舍設施，尤其添置實驗室等科研設備，又呼籲大學優先考慮創科需要。<br />\n<br />\n另外，政府已推出的科技人才入境計劃，陳茂波稱至今已批出超過200個配額，政府將於今年上半年檢討推行細節。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波說，研究員計劃至今已資助逾3700名本地畢業生加入創科發展，政府將即日起提高研究員的每月津貼額，持有學士學位的研究員，每月津貼會由1.6萬元提高至1.8萬元；持有碩士學位的研究員則由1.9萬元提高至2.1萬元。<br />\n<br />\n政府亦會即日起將研究員計劃及博士專才庫的資助期上限，由2年延長至3年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190227/s00001/1551239871246/【財政預算案】即日起提高創科研究員津貼-資助中學獲100萬元買it設備\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190227%2Fs00001%2F1551239871246%2F%E3%80%90%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E3%80%91%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%A5%E8%B5%B7%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E5%89%B5%E7%A7%91%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%93%A1%E6%B4%A5%E8%B2%BC-%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%8D%B2100%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%B2%B7it%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6fkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=5b95e525\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190227%2Fs00001%2F1551239871246%2F%E3%80%90%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E3%80%91%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%A5%E8%B5%B7%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E5%89%B5%E7%A7%91%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%93%A1%E6%B4%A5%E8%B2%BC-%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%8D%B2100%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%B2%B7it%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99&h=6cdf2e68\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190227/s00001/1551239871246/【財政預算案】即日起提高創科研究員津貼-資助中學獲100萬元買it設備</a>"},{"pid":"450b12b331bf57415cfef503ee5d5ee1d0c464c8","tid":1038922,"uid":55597,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:10:48.000Z","msg":"買 5000 塊 Raspberry Pi"},{"pid":"7f5dca658a7f9c5a76d994eac9a1b3d081a2d2a5","tid":1038922,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:41:36.000Z","msg":"Hk no it"},{"pid":"d6e7592ee2632b740562de39286b5b9d2e80529b","tid":1038922,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:44:36.000Z","msg":"買多一套<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181129/s00001/abf9e302b3b8583a4e8a60a35ca20cbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181129%2Fs00001%2Fabf9e302b3b8583a4e8a60a35ca20cbc.jpg&h=de69bbc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88440328083d7582734cf050f7877494808cac3c","tid":1038922,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:49:12.000Z","msg":"學Computer Graphics<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190224/640_a0eaa949bce67f97929400b7f56bf93d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190224%2F640_a0eaa949bce67f97929400b7f56bf93d.jpg&h=8925dc63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55715268dfaaf71b03238763175f0a2e0f18f651","tid":1038922,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T10:05:32.000Z","msg":"個100萬好快就會以各種名目移去其他野"},{"pid":"28c1b9eaf6d73b26520db67816909f303d1b2a74","tid":1038922,"uid":52276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T10:16:28.000Z","msg":"IT仔又贏"},{"pid":"9e1894b797eb1250340bb5731d0cec2a1118f3c3","tid":1038922,"uid":130695,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T10:20:00.000Z","msg":"香港政府搞IT，哈<br />\n係咪全體轉用華為 下載刁帝語錄就係？"},{"pid":"758facde6dd169d79b1dee5aebb80ae3d27dad99","tid":1038922,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T10:51:21.000Z","msg":"全部買哂iphone , iPad , Mac 機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c16c75bc632b6257f345d8bc8d380b34c238d5","tid":1038922,"uid":57787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T10:54:08.000Z","msg":"資助學校買IT嘢就令我諗起以前做過小學IT嘅膠事...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話說其中一個學期尾IT主任突然發覺有筆十萬蚊嘅預算無用到...<br />\n佢哋驚如果唔用下年就申請唔到預算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當時Win 8都就嚟出，但係全校仲用緊XP機<br />\n但係佢哋為求盡快用咗筆錢，寧願用嚟買咗八十隻叫投票蛋嘅垃圾都唔幫學校換機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n堆垃圾用嚟畀學生玩投票/MC題，但係無老師鍾意用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只會喺教育局嚟觀課嘅時候拎出嚟show off<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但最垃圾嘅地方係要用電蕊...我試過半年唔拆電蕊嘅話就已經漏晒電漿...<br />\n搞到每次用完我就要逐隻拆，到下次又要逐隻入返...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多老師根本求穩定就算，你畀筆錢佢哋都唔會用嚟諗點幫到學校升級...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390f3aacdc5dd7130b3f69ed7bf6600434ef43eb","tid":1038922,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T11:35:42.000Z","msg":"起碼收兩成回佣"},{"pid":"10c089e04d5221f06528ae67e688c63928555f62","tid":1038922,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"390f3aacdc5dd7130b3f69ed7bf6600434ef43eb","tid":1038922,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T11:35:42.000Z","msg":"起碼收兩成回佣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T11:50:24.000Z","msg":"咁易咩<br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n上年學校有200 萬qef stem撥款<br />\n都未洗過<br />\n今年又嚟100 萬<br />\n<br />\n我都想落到dd落袋"}]}